@TodoApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5218
@access_token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Health check (no authentication required)
GET {{TodoApi_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Info endpoint - Check configuration (development only)
GET {{TodoApi_HostAddress}}/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all todos
GET {{TodoApi_HostAddress}}/api/todos
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Create a new todo
POST {{TodoApi_HostAddress}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Testaa Todo API",
  "description": "Testaa että Todo API toimii Azure SQL tietokannan kanssa",
  "isCompleted": false
}

###

### Get completed todos
GET {{TodoApi_HostAddress}}/api/todos/completed
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get pending todos
GET {{TodoApi_HostAddress}}/api/todos/pending
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Update todo (replace {id} with actual todo ID)
PUT {{TodoApi_HostAddress}}/api/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Päivitetty Todo",
  "description": "Todo on nyt päivitetty",
  "isCompleted": true
}

###

### Delete todo (replace {id} with actual todo ID)
DELETE {{TodoApi_HostAddress}}/api/todos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### WeatherForecast (for testing basic API functionality)
GET {{TodoApi_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###
